<ul>
<li>Brookside</li>
<li>Belvedere Mill House</li>
<li>Chalford Place</li>
<li>Chestnut House (Smarts Mill House)</li>
<li>Green Court</li>
<li>Old Valley Inn (formerly Clothier's Arms)</li>
<li>Sevilles House</li>
<li>Springfield House</li>
